{"visible": {"type": 0, "list_id": 0}, "created_at": "Sat Jun 25 20:38:50 +0800 2022", "id": "4784347226312252", "mid": "4784347226312252", "can_edit": false, "show_additional_indication": 0, "text": "<a  href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/p/index?extparam=%E7%8E%8B%E9%9B%A8%E5%9F%8E&containerid=100808d53f06d708332e454cce711e6d5d700a&luicode=20000061&lfid=4784347226312252\" data-hide=\"\"><span class='url-icon'><img style='width: 1rem;height: 1rem' src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/photo/5213b46e/20180926/timeline_card_small_super_default.png'></span><span class=\"surl-text\">王雨城</span></a> <br />《彷徨•铲屎记》<br />今天找朋友帮拍照，代价是帮她的猫铲屎<br />我心想，这有什么难的<br /><br />看到猫砂盆，我才意识到，我中计了<br />别人铲屎是在猫砂里找屎，而我是在屎里找猫砂<br />放眼望去，无从下铲，有些地方要用凿的<br />铲了十分钟后，我开始后悔，没有用筷子<span class=\"url-icon\"><img alt=[微笑] src=\"https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_hehe-0be7e6251f.png\" style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\" /></span><br />我要是把仅剩的猫砂夹出来，这一盆可以直接扔了<br />她家猫蹲在旁边看了老半天，内心OS：我去，这是什么新鲜操作呀，我有生以来也是第一次见呀，猫砂…还需要铲的吗？<br />可以看得出来，有些已经变成化石了，没法想象她家猫怎么忍得下去<br />我要是她家猫，现在已经学会蹲马桶了<br />铲完以后，提起一袋猫屎，起码有十几二十公斤，当下我就做了二十个弯举<br />下楼的时候，我想这要是黄金，我都已经开始看汤臣一品的楼盘了", "textLength": 621, "source": "王雨城超话", "favorited": false, "pic_ids": ["008pnzbKly1h3kr0dfzp4j30v91von9x", "008pnzbKly1h3kr0msgevj30u01sygxv", "008pnzbKly1h3kr0xmot7j30u01sy15i", "008pnzbKly1h3kr1aen0qj30u01syal7"], "thumbnail_pic": "https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/thumbnail/008pnzbKly1h3kr0dfzp4j30v91von9x.jpg", "bmiddle_pic": "http://wx4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/008pnzbKly1h3kr0dfzp4j30v91von9x.jpg", "original_pic": "https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/008pnzbKly1h3kr0dfzp4j30v91von9x.jpg", "is_paid": false, "mblog_vip_type": 0, "user": {"id": 7704087868, "screen_name": "王雨城Andy", "profile_image_url": "https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.828.828.180/008pnzbKly8h2ycoz9cyaj30n00n0dhm.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&Expires=1662562561&ssig=Okj5p6VaIG", "profile_url": "https://m.weibo.cn/u/7704087868?uid=7704087868&luicode=20000061&lfid=4784347226312252", "statuses_count": 138, "verified": true, "verified_ty