{"visible": {"type": 0, "list_id": 0}, "created_at": "Wed Jan 19 12:13:10 +0800 2022", "id": "4727325076489519", "mid": "4727325076489519", "can_edit": false, "show_additional_indication": 0, "text": "进到小屋那天开心，大家都非常nice，而且还特别有梗！我当天应该是头笑飞了，但可能是剪辑师为了保护我的形象没剪进去哈哈哈<span class=\"url-icon\"><img alt=[哈哈] src=\"https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_haha-0ec05e6dad.png\" style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\" /></span><br />有很多网友问我这个年龄为什么来半熟而不是去心动的信号，我这里给一个标准答案。半熟找到我的时候碰巧比较有空，也觉得是很新奇的体验，我也想要破圈，就直接去面试了。<br />另外，我并不后悔来这个节目。我其实也是恋综老观众了，对比众多其他恋综，半熟的氛围简直不要太好！我太喜欢这儿了！<br />最后，感谢网友们P的图<a  href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/p/index?extparam=%E5%8D%8A%E7%86%9F%E6%81%8B%E4%BA%BA&containerid=1008085975e519b8f3f14c452addba3b0ec634&luicode=20000061&lfid=4727325076489519\" data-hide=\"\"><span class='url-icon'><img style='width: 1rem;height: 1rem' src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/photo/5213b46e/20180926/timeline_card_small_super_default.png'></span><span class=\"surl-text\">半熟恋人</span></a><a  href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/p/index?extparam=%E7%8E%8B%E9%9B%A8%E5%9F%8E&containerid=100808d53f06d708332e454cce711e6d5d700a&luicode=20000061&lfid=4727325076489519\" data-hide=\"\"><span class='url-icon'><img style='width: 1rem;height: 1rem' src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/photo/5213b46e/20180926/timeline_card_small_super_default.png'></span><span class=\"surl-text\">王雨城</span></a><a  href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8D%8A%E7%86%9F%E6%81%8B%E4%BA%BA%23&extparam=%23%E5%8D%8A%E7%86%9F%E6%81%8B%E4%BA%BA%23&luicode=20000061&lfid=4727325076489519\" data-hide=\"\"><span class=\"surl-text\">#半熟恋人#</span></a>", "textLength": 454, "source": "王雨城超话", "favorited": false, "pic_ids": ["008pnzbKly1gyiutvn1naj30u01hwk8v", "008pnzbKly1gyiutvylo4j31l70wi11z", "008pnzbKly1gyiutv9d0nj31lc0wiqbk", "008pnzbKly1gyiutw9hvnj30zk0k340e", "008pnzbKly1gyiutwgpsqj30c80cdaar", "008pnzbKly1gyiutwntjoj30c80cqmxu", "008pnzbKly1gyiutxm94mj31ds0n0tql", "008pnzbKly1gyiutyv2hfj31ds0n04my", "008pnzbKly1gyiut