{"visible": {"type": 0, "list_id": 0}, "created_at": "Fri Jan 21 01:11:23 +0800 2022", "id": "4727883308992178", "mid": "4727883308992178", "edit_count": 1, "can_edit": false, "edit_at": "Fri Jan 21 01:43:41 +0800 2022", "show_additional_indication": 0, "text": "聊到广西口音，大家突然玩起了“广西表妹”的梗，哈哈哈<span class=\"url-icon\"><img alt=[笑cry] src=\"https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_xiaoku-f2bd11b506.png\" style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\" /></span><br />作为广西人也是哭笑不得，虽然挺有趣的，但不得不说，不是所有广西人都这么讲话的<span class=\"url-icon\"><img alt=[并不简单] src=\"https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png\" style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\" /></span>至少我在桂林没有听到过。<br />只有部分地区有一点这个调调，很多短视频是为了搞笑进行了夸张化的加工。希望大家不要对广西口音有这个刻板印象噢<span class=\"url-icon\"><img alt=[哈哈] src=\"https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_haha-0ec05e6dad.png\" style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\" /></span>适度玩梗就好<br />头发长了没空去剪，近期出门先戴个帽子吧 <br /><a  href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/p/index?extparam=%E5%8D%8A%E7%86%9F%E6%81%8B%E4%BA%BA&containerid=1008085975e519b8f3f14c452addba3b0ec634&luicode=20000061&lfid=4727883308992178\" data-hide=\"\"><span class='url-icon'><img style='width: 1rem;height: 1rem' src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/photo/5213b46e/20180926/timeline_card_small_super_default.png'></span><span class=\"surl-text\">半熟恋人</span></a> <a  href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/p/index?extparam=%E7%8E%8B%E9%9B%A8%E5%9F%8E&containerid=100808d53f06d708332e454cce711e6d5d700a&luicode=20000061&lfid=4727883308992178\" data-hide=\"\"><span class='url-icon'><img style='width: 1rem;height: 1rem' src='https://n.sinaimg.cn/photo/5213b46e/20180926/timeline_card_small_super_default.png'></span><span class=\"surl-text\">王雨城</span></a> <a  href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8D%8A%E7%86%9F%E6%81%8B%E4%BA%BA%23&extparam=%23%E5%8D%8A%E7%86%9F%E6%81%8B%E4%BA%BA%23&luicode=20000061&lfid=4727883308992178\" data-hide=\"\"><span class=\"surl-text\">#半熟恋人#</span></a>", "textLength": 378, "source